---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const CALENDLY_URL = 'https://calendly.com/derek-beitz-soloex/30min';
const LINKEDIN_DEREK = 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/derekbeitz/';
const LINKEDIN_CO = 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/soloex-io/';

const pageDesc = 'Soloex is a Salesforce and HubSpot consultancy founded by Derek and Kristin Beitz in Mechanicsburg, PA. Women-owned, WBENC certified. Built by the person who will actually build your CRM.';
---

<Layout title="About — Soloex.io" description={pageDesc} active="about">

  <section class="section-hero">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>How Soloex started.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-compact">
    <div class="container-narrow prose">
      <p>Derek spent years as the technical closer at a Summit-tier Salesforce Partner. When a sales team needed someone to walk a client through the hard parts, he was the person they pulled onto the call. He'd win the business, then do the actual work — business analysis, solution architecture, the build itself, training, and the inevitable upsell a few months later.</p>

      <p>He was doing every part of the job. Now it was time to go out on his own.</p>

      <p>In August 2024, Derek and his wife Kristin went full-time on Soloex. He does the work he was already doing — just directly, for the client. Kristin runs operations, books, and billing.</p>

      <p>Women-owned, WBENC certified. The bet is simple: when you hire Soloex, you hire the person who's going to build it. Not a pitch deck. Not a junior handed your project after the closer signs.</p>

      <p class="pull">The same person who used to get pulled onto closing calls to provide the confidence that won the business in the first place.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tinted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">The team</p>
        <h2>Two people. Every email answered.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="card team-card">
          <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Derek headshot. Replace gradient avatar with <img src="/derek.jpg" alt="Derek Beitz, founder of Soloex" class="team-avatar" />. -->
          <div class="team-avatar team-avatar-derek" aria-hidden="true">DB</div>
          <h3>Derek Beitz</h3>
          <div class="team-role">Founder &amp; Technical Lead</div>
          <p>Salesforce and HubSpot certified. Former consultant at a Summit-tier Salesforce Partner. Member of Salesforce's Automotive Cloud beta testing program. Leads every client engagement from discovery through go-live.</p>
          <a href={LINKEDIN_DEREK} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-link">LinkedIn →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card team-card">
          <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Kristin headshot. Gray circle for now. Replace with <img src="/kristin.jpg" alt="Kristin Beitz, co-founder of Soloex" class="team-avatar" />. -->
          <div class="team-avatar team-avatar-gray" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <h3>Kristin Beitz</h3>
          <div class="team-role">Co-founder &amp; Operations</div>
          <p>Runs operations, books, and billing. The reason Derek stays in the technical work instead of the spreadsheet. Women-owned, WBENC certified.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="sub-h2">Our credentials</h2>
      <ul class="credentials">
        <li>
          <strong>WBENC certified women-owned business</strong>
          <span>Registered through WBENC. Eligible for supplier-diversity procurement programs.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Certified Salesforce Partner</strong>
          <span>Five active certifications across Sales Cloud, Service Cloud, Marketing Cloud, Account Engagement, and more.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Top Rated Plus on Upwork</strong>
          <span>★ 5.0 rating · 100% Job Success · Top Rated Plus (top 3% of freelancers globally).</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Salesforce Automotive Cloud beta partner</strong>
          <span>Member of Salesforce's Automotive Cloud beta testing program.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-tinted">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="sub-h2">How we work</h2>
      <p class="muted-p">Every engagement follows the same six steps — kickoff, discovery, scope, build, go live, support. The order never changes. The transparency never changes. You always know where you are.</p>
      <a href="/process" class="inline-link">See the full process →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="sub-h2">Who we work with</h2>
      <div class="facts">
        <div>
          <div class="fact-label">Company size</div>
          <p>Up to 500 employees. Sweet spot is SMB and lower mid-market.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="fact-label">Industries</div>
          <p>Agnostic. Projects span universities, healthcare, tech, landscaping, automotive, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="fact-label">Geography</div>
          <p>Primarily US. Open to international. Based in Mechanicsburg, PA.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="fact-label">Who we talk to</div>
          <p>Founders, owners, VPs, and directors with budget authority.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-dark final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Want to talk?</h2>
      <p class="final-cta-subhead">Free 30-minute call. Tell us what's broken.</p>
      <a href={CALENDLY_URL} class="btn btn-light btn-large" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fix my CRM →</a>
      <div class="final-cta-meta">
        <a href={LINKEDIN_CO} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Soloex on LinkedIn →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .prose p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .prose p.pull {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--color-ink-700);
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .team-card { text-align: center; padding: 36px 28px; }
  .team-avatar {
    width: 112px;
    height: 112px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }
  .team-avatar-derek {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-ink-500) 0%, var(--color-ink-700) 100%);
  }
  .team-avatar-gray { background: #D6DEE6; }
  .team-role {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-ink-500);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 6px 0 14px;
  }

  .sub-h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 2.4vw, 30px); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .muted-p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 14px; }

  .credentials { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; }
  .credentials li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .credentials li:first-child { border-top: 0; }
  .credentials li strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .credentials li span { color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 14px; }

  .facts {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px 40px;
  }
  .fact-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-ink-500);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .inline-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-ink-700);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 4px;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .inline-link:hover { transform: translateX(2px); }

  .final-cta { text-align: center; padding: 96px 0; }
  .final-cta h2 { color: #FFFFFF; }
  .final-cta-subhead {
    color: var(--color-ink-300);
    font-size: 17px;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 16px auto 28px;
  }
  .final-cta-meta { margin-top: 28px; font-size: 13px; }
  .final-cta-meta a { color: var(--color-ink-300); }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .team-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; }
    .credentials li { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4px; }
    .facts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
